## SSE Event Format (Never Change This)
```
event: token
data: {"content": "text here"}

event: citation
data: {"source": "file.pdf", "page": 4, "score": 0.94}

event: done
data: {"conversation_id": "uuid", "cost_usd": 0}
```
The frontend `useChat.ts` expects EXACTLY this format.
